OL,3,C'Traumatised' family say house needs
OL,4,Cprotection after double crash
OL,6,FA family from Stourbridge is calling
OL,7,Fon Dudley Council to implement urgent
OL,8,Froad safety measures after two serious
OL,9,Fcrashes near their home.
OL,11,FThe family says they are living in
OL,12,Ffear and struggling to sleep due to
OL,13,Fthe ongoing danger posed by speeding
OL,14,Fvehicles on the bend where they live.
OL,16,FThe first crash, which happened in
OL,17,FJuly last year, caused significant
OL,18,Fdamage to the front of their house.
