OL,3,C'Traumatised' family say house needs
OL,4,Cprotection after double crash
OL,6,FWendy Skelding described the
OL,7,Fterrifying moment: "My daughter was in
OL,8,Fthe kitchen when the car came off the
OL,9,Fbend and crashed into the house.
OL,11,F"If my grandchildren had been in the
OL,12,Fliving room, it could have been much
OL,13,Fworse."
OL,15,FMost recently, another vehicle crashed
OL,16,Finto the family's parked car on the
OL,17,Fsame road leaving it impossible to
OL,18,Fdrive.
