OL,3,C'Traumatised' family say house needs
OL,4,Cprotection after double crash
OL,6,FDespite the family's concerns, Dudley
OL,7,FCouncil has stated that it does not
OL,8,Fplan to introduce further traffic
OL,9,Fcalming measures on Hayes Lane.
OL,11,FCouncillor Damian Corfield, cabinet
OL,12,Fmember for environment and highways,
OL,13,Fnoted: "We are aware of the incidents
OL,14,Fand are in contact with the residents.
OL,16,F"We undertook a 7-day speed survey,
OL,17,Fwhich showed that the majority of
OL,18,Fvehicles were within 31.9mph, within
OL,19,Ftolerance for the 30mph speed limit."
