OL,3,C'Traumatised' family say house needs
OL,4,Cprotection after double crash
OL,6,FHe added, "There are already road
OL,7,Fmarkings advising drivers to slow
OL,8,Fdown, and the road surface has been
OL,9,Ftreated to help drivers maintain
OL,10,Fcontrol on this gradient.
OL,12,F"Given the available data, there are
OL,13,Fno current plans to introduce
OL,14,Fadditional measures."
OL,16,FHowever, the Skelding family remains
OL,17,Fconcerned that the road remains
OL,18,Fdangerous, particularly for
OL,19,Fpedestrians and nearby residents.
