OL,3,C'Traumatised' family say house needs
OL,4,Cprotection after double crash
OL,6,FWendy Skelding voiced the family's
OL,7,Fongoing fears: "It's terrifying living
OL,8,Fhere. Every night we worry about the
OL,9,Fnext crash."
OL,11,FThe council has stated that while
OL,12,Fspeed enforcement falls under the
OL,13,Fjurisdiction of the police, they are
OL,14,Fworking closely with local policing
OL,15,Fteams to identify persistent speeding
OL,16,Foffenders.
OL,18,FMeanwhile, the Skelding family
OL,19,Fcontinues to press for bollards or
OL,20,Fflashing signs to prevent further
OL,21,Faccidents and avoid future tragedies.
